38:35.640 --> 38:37.240
Jangan sibuk, biar dia buat.

38:37.520 --> 38:38.120
Mari, mari.

38:38.120 --> 38:39.720
Basuh tangan, kita nak makan dah.

38:39.720 --> 38:40.560
