39:52.920 --> 39:53.680
Dia dah lama duduk di sana.

39:53.680 --> 39:55.420
Tak eloklah macam ni.

39:56.360 --> 39:58.490
Hidang lauk, hidang lauk, hidangkan.

39:58.880 --> 39:59.810
Pakcik, makcik.

40:00.520 --> 40:01.780
